snippet.title: How To Make Charcoal At Home - कोयले से पैसे कमाये | Very Easy
snippet.description:
Charcoal From Wood ...घर पर कोयला कैसे बनाये....In This Video We Made Charcoal At Home Using Only Woods.

Ye Bhi Check Karo - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ApzXZ9LzKes&list=PLs2q0kQKcqma0C44OiJUdaOSoC61Bmloe

SUBSCRIBE : https://youtube.com/MRINDIANHACKER?sub_confirmation=1

FOLLOW KARLO 😘
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/dilraj_singh_rawat
Twitter : https://www.x.com/MR_INDIANHACKER
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/mrindianhacker00

Imagine charcoal as a tiny superhero with lots of holes in its suit. These holes act like magnets, grabbing bad guys like dirt, yucky chemicals, and even bad breath germs!
Here's what this charcoal superhero can do:
1 - Shiny teeth: When you brush with charcoal toothpaste, the superhero grabs stainy yummies stuck on your teeth, making them pearly white!
2 - Happy tummy: If you ever eat something that doesn't agree with you, charcoal can suck up the bad stuff before it makes your tummy grumpy!
3 - Clean skin: Like a tiny vacuum, charcoal in face masks grabs dirt and oil that can clog your pores, leaving your skin smooth and happy.
4 - Fresh air: Special charcoal filters can grab tiny stinky things from the air, making it smell clean and fresh, like after a summer rain!
Remember: Like any superhero, charcoal needs to be used carefully. Always ask a grown-up before trying anything new, and never eat charcoal unless it's made for food!

So there you have it, the amazing world of charcoal, the tiny superhero with holes! Pretty cool, right?

Thanks for watching! Love you Titanium Army

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2 | Flowers | EP# 424
snippet.description:
പാറമട വീട്ടില്‍ ശബരിമലയിലേക്ക് പോകാനുള്ള ഒരുക്കങ്ങള്‍ നടക്കുകയാണ്. ബാലുവിനും കേശുവിനും ഒപ്പം ഇത്തവണ പാറുക്കുട്ടിയും സന്നിധാനത്തേക്ക് പോകുകയാണ്. പമ്പയിലെ തിരക്കിനിടയില്‍ പാറുവിനെ നോക്കാനുള്ള ഉത്തരവാദിത്വം കേശുവിനാണ്. പാറമട വീട്ടില്‍ ഇനി ഭക്തിസാന്ദ്രമായ ദിനങ്ങള്‍.

Paramada household is prepping for the pilgrimage to Sabarimala. Parkutty also accompanies Balu and Keshu this time. The responsibility to take care of Parukutty amid the crowd in Pamba has been bestowed upon Keshu. Days of utmost holiness and spirituality to fill Paramada house. 'Keep watching Uppum Mulakum'

snippet.title: PREGNANCY പഠിപ്പിച്ച വലിയ പാഠം | @dimplerose4417 | Josh Talks Malayalam
snippet.description:
#joshtalksmalayalam #dimplerose #motherhood #womenempowerment 

പഠിച്ചുകൊണ്ട് വളരൂ ജോഷ് Talks-ലൂടെ- നിങ്ങളുടെ Communication Skills മെച്ചപ്പെടുത്താൻ, ജോഷ് ടോക്സിന്റെ Malayalam to English app-ൽ ചേരുക: https://bit.ly/JoshTalksMalayalamToEnglish

ഡിംപിൾ റോസ് @dimplerose4417  എന്ന ARTIST -നെ സിനിമകളിലൂടെയും സീരിയലുകളിലൂടെയും ഒരുപാട് മലയാളികൾക്ക് പരിചിതയായ മുഖമാണ്. ഒരു ബാലതാരമായി തുടങ്ങി,  പ്രധാന വേഷങ്ങൾ ചെയ്യുന്നതുവരെ, ഡിംപിൾ വീട്ടിലെ ഒരു അംഗമെന്നോണം എല്ലാവര്ക്കും പ്രിയപ്പെട്ടവളായി. എന്നിരുന്നാലും, ജീവിതത്തിന്റെ ഒരു ഘട്ടത്തിൽ ഡിംപിളിന് എന്ത് സംഭവിച്ചുവെന്ന് പലർക്കും അറിയുമായിരിക്കില്ല? ഈ #joshtalks -ൽ, തന്റെ ഗർഭകാലത്തെ ഹൃദയഭേദകമായ അനുഭവം ഡിംപിൾ പങ്കുവെക്കുന്നു. നമ്മുടെ സമൂഹത്തിലെ പല സ്ത്രീകളും നേരിടുന്ന പ്രയാസങ്ങളെ ഡിംപിൾ തന്റെ ടോൾകിലൂടെ അവതരിപ്പിക്കുന്നു. താൻ അനുഭവിച്ച ജീവിതത്തിന്റെ ഏറ്റവും ദുഷ്‌കരമായ അവസ്ഥയിൽ നിന്ന് പാഠങ്ങൾ ഉൾക്കൊണ്ട് തനിക്കുണ്ടായ സ്വയം പരിവർത്തനത്തെക്കുറിച്ചും ഡിംപിൾ പറയുന്നു. ഡിംപിളിനെപ്പോലെ നമുക്കുനേരെ വരുന്ന വെല്ലുവിളികളെ നമ്മുടെ താഴ്ച്ചയും ഉയർച്ചയും മനസ്സിലാക്കാനും അതിനനുസരിച്ച് പ്രവർത്തിക്കാനുമുള്ള അവസരമായി കാണണം. 

Dimple Rose @dimplerose4417  is a much familiar face to a lot of Malayali's for her presence in #movie and #serial . From a child artist to doing main roles, Dimple has been a like a close member in many households. However, many people don't know about what happened to Dimple at one point of her life? In her #joshtalks , she shares the heart wrenching experience of her #pregnancyjourney .Many women in our society face a lot of things that Dimple conveys in her talk. She also talks about the #selftransformation  that she had after this #pregnancy  by taking the #learnings from the toughest situation life put her in. Like Dimple, we also should see the challenges thrown to us as an opportunity to understand our lows and highs and work accordingly.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com- ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.

If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com, if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayali's by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayali's. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

ജോഷ് Talks ഇന്ത്യയിലെ ഏറ്റവും പ്രേരണാത്മകമായ കഥകൾ ശേഖരിക്കുകയും അവ പങ്കുവെക്കാൻ ഒരു വേദി നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുന്നു. വിവിധ പശ്ചാത്തലങ്ങളിൽ നിന്നുള്ള അനുഭവസ്ഥർ, അവരുടെ സംഘർഷഭരിത കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ചെറുതായി തുടങ്ങിയ ജോഷ് Talks, നിലവിൽ 9 ഭാഷകളിൽ കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ  നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം.
#joshtalks #deliverystory #mother #baby  #family

snippet.title: Reality Of BIG BOSS - Aishwariya's Untold Stories on Bharti TV
snippet.description:
🎙️ Brace yourselves for the most candid, unfiltered episode yet on Bharti TV! Join the laughter riot as the dynamic comedy couple, Bharti and Harsh, sit down with the recently eliminated Big Boss contestant, Aishwariya, for a no-holds-barred conversation on all things Big Boss.😂 Get ready for a rollercoaster of emotions and laughter as Aishwariya spills the beans on her rollercoaster journey inside the Big Boss house. From the dramatic confrontations to the hilarious behind-the-scenes antics, this podcast is your backstage pass to the real world of Big Boss. 👀 Tune in to witness Aishwariya's journey like never before, as Bharti and Harsh add their unique comedic flair to the narrative. Subscribe now and get ready for a hilarious, eye-opening ride through the ups and downs of the Big Boss house.🎉 Don't miss out on the fun – hit that subscribe button, grab your popcorn, and join Bharti and Harsh as they bring you the unfiltered reality of Big Boss, one laugh at a time! 🌈

snippet.title: Truck Drivers' Strike Ends After Centre-AIMTC Meet | Why Did They Protest?
snippet.description:
The truck drivers had been protesting against Section 106(2) of the Bharatiya Nyaya Sanhita for the past two days. The new provision in the BNS regarding hit-and-run cases includes a punishment of 10 years imprisonment and a fine of up to 7 lakh rupees. The protestors were concerned that this new provision might lead to unjust punishments such as mob violence. They also believed that the government should have consulted with stakeholders before making such a decision. However, the strike was called off after a meeting between Home Secretary Ajay Bhalla and the representative of All India Motor Transport Congress. To know more about why the protest was called off, watch the video.
#truckdriver #strike #news

snippet.title: Ayodhya Ram Mandir History | अयोध्या विवाद की पूरी कहानी| Ram Mandir Inauguration | RJ Raunac
snippet.description:
---------------------------------------------
Step into the complex tapestry of Ayodhya's history as we embark on a journey through centuries of controversy, leading up to the historic inauguration of the Ayodhya temple in 2024. This video meticulously traces the origins of the Ayodhya temple dispute, capturing the myriad events and perspectives that have shaped this enduring controversy.

Introduction:
Our narrative begins in 1528 when the Babri Masjid was constructed in Ayodhya by the Mughal emperor Babur. This marked the genesis of a dispute that would reverberate through the annals of Indian history for centuries to come.

The Mughal Era:
Explore the Mughal era as we delve into the architectural marvel of the Babri Masjid and the historical context that surrounded its construction. Uncover the socio-political landscape of the time, where the seeds of the Ayodhya dispute were sown.

Colonial Influence:
Fast forward to the colonial era, and witness how British rule intensified religious tensions surrounding the Ayodhya dispute. The East India Company's policies exacerbated communal divisions, laying the groundwork for future conflicts.

Post-Independence Period:
As India gained independence in 1947, the Ayodhya dispute took on a new dimension. Discover the evolving dynamics between Hindus and Muslims, and the legal battles that ensued over the possession of the disputed site.

Babri Masjid Demolition (1992):
The pivotal moment in the Ayodhya saga unfolds as we explore the controversial demolition of the Babri Masjid in 1992. Analyze the events leading up to this fateful day and the aftermath that shook the nation, sparking widespread communal tensions.

Legal Battles:
Navigate through the labyrinth of legal proceedings as various parties sought resolution through the courts. From the Liberhan Commission to the Allahabad High Court verdict of 2010, understand the legal intricacies that shaped the Ayodhya dispute.

Landmark Supreme Court Judgment (2019):
In 2019, the Supreme Court of India delivered a historic verdict, bringing a semblance of closure to the Ayodhya dispute. Uncover the key elements of the judgment and the principles that guided the court's decision, offering insights into the culmination of decades-long legal battles.

Construction of the Ayodhya Temple:
The video then transitions to the present, capturing the excitement and significance surrounding the inauguration of the Ayodhya temple in 2024. Witness the meticulous planning, architectural grandeur, and the emotional resonance as a symbol of unity and cultural heritage is reborn.

Reconciliation and Moving Forward:
Finally, reflect on the lessons learned from the Ayodhya temple dispute and explore the prospects of communal harmony and reconciliation in post-inauguration Ayodhya. Discover the efforts made by various communities to bridge gaps and foster a spirit of unity.

Conclusion:
As we conclude this comprehensive exploration of the Ayodhya temple dispute, gain a nuanced understanding of the historical, cultural, and legal facets that have defined this complex narrative. Join us in commemorating the inauguration of the Ayodhya temple as a momentous chapter in Indian history, embodying the resilience of a nation in the face of enduring controversies.

Maa Nahi Saas Hoon Main Episode 63 - [Eng Sub] - Hammad Shoaib - Sumbul Iqbal - Farhan Ally Agha - 4th January 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

This story revolves around Mehreen and her daughter Areej, who was born after years of prayers. Prior to her birth, Mehreen and her husband had been caring for Salman, Areej's cousin. However, a tragedy struck, separating Areej from her family. Afterwards, Mehreen decided to raise Salman as her own son.
Years later, Salman crosses paths with Urooj, a beautiful and fearless girl, the daughter of school teacher Shoaib and his wife Naseem. Initially resistant to Salman's advances, Urooj eventually falls in love with him. Unbeknownst to Salman and his family, Urooj is none other than Areej, Mehreen's long-lost daughter.
Will Urooj discover the truth about her identity? How will the family come to know that Urooj is Mehreen’s long-lost daughter, Areej? How will Urooj react when she gets to know that Mehreen is her real mother? What impact will Urooj’s identity have on Salman? Will Mehreen accept Urooj as her daughter? Will Urooj’s true identity pose a threat to her relationship with Salman?

snippet.title: C-TET | गद्यांश | Episode- 1 | Sanskritganga | Sarwagya Bhooshan |
snippet.description:
🔶 नमः संस्कृताय 🙏
संस्कृतगङ्गा चैनल पर आप सभी संस्कृत प्रेमियों का हृदय से स्वागत एवं अभिनन्दन है। 
मित्रों विभिन्न संस्कृत पाठ्यक्रमों पर आधारित नया बैच प्रारम्भ हो गया है,आप सभी अधिक से अधिक संख्या मे जुड़ कर इसका लाभ उठाइए और अपने सभी मित्रों तक इसकी सूचना अवश्य दें। 

👉अभी अपनी तैयारी प्रारम्भ करें , भारत के नम्बर 1 संस्कृत शिक्षण केंद्र संस्कृतगंगा के साथ जुड़कर आप भी अपने शिक्षक बनने के सपने को साकार करें। तो देर किस बात की, अभी सम्पर्क करें संस्कृतगंगा कार्यालय में और अपने लक्ष्य को एक बेहतर दिशा दें।

==================================================================नए बैच से जुड़ने हेतु सम्पर्क करें- 8004545091, 7800138404, 9839852033, 7800134448
====================================================================
🔶 कुछ अन्य तथ्य -
👉 प्रिय मित्रों संस्कृतगंगा का मुख्य उद्देश्य संस्कृत भाषा को जन-जन तक पहुचाना है, और सभी ऐसे अभ्यर्थी जो किसी कारणवश पढ़ाई नहीं कर पा रहे हैं, उनको भी इस ऑनलाइन क्लास के माध्यम से शिक्षा एवं रोजगार प्रदान कराना है ।

 👉 संस्कृतगंगा संस्कृत शिक्षा के क्षेत्र में क्रान्ति लाने के लिए कटिबद्ध है। पिछले 12 वर्षों से संस्कृतगंगा शिक्षा समिति निःस्वार्थ भाव से कई हजार विद्यार्थियों को संस्कृत में रोजगार दिला चुकी है और आगे भी यह यात्रा अनवरत जारी है।  
 
👉 2011 से शुरुवाती कुछ वर्षों तक निःशुल्क तथा बाद में नाम मात्र की शुल्क पर विद्यार्थियों के हितार्थ संचालित संस्कृतगंगा संस्था की यात्रा अभी भी अनवरत जारी है।  

 👉 वर्तमान में संस्कृत सम्बन्धी विभिन्न प्रतियोगी परीक्षाओं से सम्बन्धित सुव्यवस्थित ऑनलाइन कोर्स हमारे  Sanskrit Ganga Official App  पर नाम मात्र की शुल्क में उपलब्ध है,जिसे आप Google Playstore से डाउनलोड कर सकते हैं। 

👉Sanskrit Ganga Official App पर अभी  2 लाख 68 हजार से अधिक Active Users हैं, जो संस्कृत के क्षेत्र में अभी तक का सर्वश्रेष्ठ कीर्तिमान है, जो कि आप सभी संस्कृत प्रेमियों के अपार स्नेह से प्राप्त हुआ है। 

👉 आप भी TGT, PGT,LT UGC-NET/JRF,UP-TET, C-TET, H-TET, MP VARG- I,II,III, IAS,PSC  जैसी समस्त संस्कृत  प्रतियोगी परीक्षाओं  में सफलता प्राप्त करने के लिए आज ही Sanskrit Ganga Official App को अपने फ़ोन में Install करें....

👉 Sanskrit Ganga Official App  पर ऑनलाइन कोर्स के माध्यम से सम्पूर्ण पाठ्यक्रम के साथ संस्कृत की पाठ्यसामग्री उपलब्ध कराई जाती है  जैसे-लाइव लैक्चर,रिकार्डेड वीडिओ ,ऑडियो E-NOTES, पीडीएफ नोट्स, सॉल्वड पेपर, ,टेस्ट सीरीज़, इत्यादि।

Baylagaam Episode 99 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Abbas - Laiba Khan - Haroon Shahid - Tuba Anwar - 4th January 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

The story centers around Ramsha, a young girl and the only child of her loving parents, Sajid and Mehnaz. Raised with affection and no restrictions, Ramsha enjoys unlimited internet access, which leads to her spending an excessive time on social media, quickly becoming her hobby.
As her fascination with social media intensifies, Ramsha's hobby evolves into an all-consuming passion for fame, prompting her to take extreme measures. During her relentless pursuit of stardom, she crosses paths with Afnan, the son of the influential businessman Qasim Ali. While Afnan, who holds affection for his paternal cousin Aleezay, views Ramsha as a source of amusement, she misinterprets their friendship as love.
Disheartened by her failed search for love, Ramsha turns towards fame. Ramsha's unwavering quest for popularity propels her onto a challenging path, causing turmoil within her family. As her popularity soars, she becomes increasingly distant from her loved ones, leading her life down a tumultuous road, where she discovers the other side of fame many people are unaware of. Along this journey, she encounters Afnan once more, but circumstances have taken a different turn.
Will Ramsha achieve the fame she so desperately desires? Will her pursuit bring dire consequences? Can she find contentment in fame instead of love? And will Ramsha's parents have to bear the consequences of her passion?

snippet.title: பொங்கல் பரிசு தொகுப்பு... அதிரடியாக பறந்த முக்கிய உத்தரவு
snippet.description:
பொங்கல் பரிசு தொகுப்பு... அதிரடியாக பறந்த முக்கிய உத்தரவு

#pongal2024 #thanthitv #minister #thanthitv 

பொங்கல் பண்டிகையையொட்டி பச்சரிசி, சர்க்கரை உள்ளிட்டவை அடங்கிய பொங்கல் பரிசு தொகுப்பினை, தமிழ்நாடு அரசு அறிவித்துள்ளது. இந்தநிலையில், பொங்கல் பரிசு தொகுப்பினை தடையின்றி வழங்குவது குறித்தும், பொது விநியோகத் திட்டத்தில் இன்றியமையாப் பொருள்கள் விநியோகம் குறித்தும், உணவு மற்றும் உணவுப்பொருள் வழங்கல் துறை அமைச்சர் சக்கரபாணி தலைமையில் ஆய்வு கூட்டம் நடைபெற்றது. அப்போது அமைச்சர் சக்கரபாணி, பொங்கல் பரிசு தொகுப்பு வழங்குவதற்கான தயார் நிலையையும், அதற்கான பொருட்களை கொள்முதல் செய்வது குறித்தும் ஆய்வு செய்து, அதிகாரிகளுக்கு ஆலோசனைகளை வழங்கினார். PADDY PROCESSING AGREEMENT மூலம், நவீன அரிசி ஆலைத் திட்டத்தினைத் துரிதப்படுத்திச் செயல்படுத்திடுமாறும், அவர் உத்தரவிட்டார்

ABOUT US: Press Information Bureau (PIB) is the nodal agency of Government of India to disseminate information to print/electronic media on government policies, programmes, initiatives and achievements. 

PIB disseminates information through press releases, press notes, photographs, videos, infographics and also through social media platforms. It also organises Press Conferences, Press Briefings, Interviews of Ministers/Senior Officers for sensitising media persons on important policy initiatives of the Government.
